Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:24:02.33,Kingdom-ED-English,,0,0,0,,I won't turn away from my tearful memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:06.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
