Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.82,0:24:47.42,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm stepping back...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:49.92,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Am I scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:52.17,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The fear of death attacks for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.17,0:24:55.68,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Xin! If you're just a sword, you'll be smashed to pieces!
